       <h2 id="Global_Network_of_AWS_Regions" class="lb-tiny-align-center lb-txt-normal lb-txt-none lb-txt-36 lb-small-v-margin lb-h2 lb-title" style="margin-top:0px;"> Global Network of AWS Regions</h2> 
       <div class="lb-tiny-align-center lb-txt-light lb-txt-none lb-txt-20 lb-txt lb-current-page-link">
         The AWS Cloud spans 105 Availability Zones within 33 geographic regions, with announced plans for 21 more Availability Zones and seven more AWS Regions in Malaysia, Mexico, New Zealand, the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, Thailand, Taiwan, and the AWS European Sovereign Cloud. 
       </div> 
      </div> 
     </div> 
    </div> 
